name: Personalized Vinyl Stickers with Digital Drawing
description:
Custom buying instructions:

Each order comes with 10 stickers professionally printed on Vinyl (3"X 3") and a digital signed image of your drawing for you to post and use however you would like.

 

1. Please select how many people are in your photo

2. Please write in the Personalization box if you would like your sticker to say anything. If you don't want text please write "NA" 

3. Please choose your Font Number in the second Custom Box


Please make sure all spelling is correct

 

After purchasing please email your photo to: info@kateandkrisshop.com

Please let us know if you have any specifics you would like included in the drawing in this email. (Example: If you have specific colors you want included, or any special small details, backround ideas)

 

We will email you back a digital proof of the design for you to approve. If we don't hear back within 72 hours, we will print and ship reguardless. Once mailed you will get a notification of your shipping number along with a digital image of your design.

 

If you want more than 10 copies, have more than three people you want on a sticker, have lots of pictures, or if you have a complicated order please feel free to email us & we will create you a customized order. 

 

Fun Ideas: Couples, Christmas cards, family pictures, friends birthday, events, themed pictures, graduation, sports themes, baby pictures, etc.

 

We ask if you post your digital art on social media to please tag us at @kateandkris  Thank you!

name: Kids - Custom Tie Dye Tee
description:
Create a customized Tie Dye T-Shirt ! 

1. Choose what size you would like

2. Choose what color Tie dye you would like.

3. Choose your color vinyl 

4.Choose your  font # 

5. In "Custom Text Box" Please write what you would like your item to say. If you don't want any text please write "N/A"

 

All choices are in product photos under the main photo. And there are a few extra color mixes to choose from as well. ("Unicorn Rainbow" & "Cotton Candy")

 

If you have any questions or a difficult or large order please feel free to reach out to us at info@kateandkrisshop.com

 

Thanks! ♡

name: Custom Tie Dye Onezie or Baby Tee
description:
Create a customized Tie Dye T-Shirt or Onezie! 

1. Choose what type of clothing & the size you would like

2. Choose what color Tie dye you would like. If you would like a Solid Color please choose "Solid Color" from the drop down and include what color you would like in the Custom Text Box. 

3. Choose your color vinyl 

4.Choose your  font # 

5. In "Custom Text Box" Please write what you would like your item to say. If you don't want any text please write "N/A"

 

All choices are in product photos under the main photo. And there are a few extra color mixes to choose from as well. ("Unicorn Rainbow" & "Cotton Candy")

 

If you have any questions or a difficult or large order please feel free to reach out to us at info@kateandkrisshop.com

 

Thanks! ♡
